1.title: The Creatine Monster
1.plot: Jimmy Russell is introduced to a whole new world when his best friend, Chesten Byes, introduces him to the dangers and glories of creatine supplementation.

imdb.plot outline: "Do You Even Lift?" is a web series about two young college students who are obsessed with the narcissistic glory of modern bodybuilding culture. Jimmy Russell and Chesten Byes fail to realize that unlike in the gym, people in the real world don't care how much they can bench press, or how low their body-fat percentages are.
